,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得我男朋友係一個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多係多條撚<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n1. 我係唔撚信星座既 佢就成日睇星座乜乜乜<br />\n睇下我同佢夾唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲同我解釋乜野叫星盤 話我只係太陽雙魚 上升係天秤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲要屌返我話我無知<br />\n<br />\n2. 每次傾到食咩 次次都係我諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =男友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你想食咩呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「無所謂 你揀啦」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「日本野？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「唔想食」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「薩利亞？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「唔食垃圾 好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「......咁你想食乜野呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你諗啦」<br />\n我諗食乜都唔係問題<br />\n問題每次嗌交佢就會講「你幾時考慮過我感受？平時你想食乜我都就晒你！你仲想點嘛八婆！」<br />\n我個刻真係心諗「你無撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n3. 前幾日同佢嗌交<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「唔想再見到你呀 唔好再搵我 我唔會再理你 走啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n於是我第二日就真係無搵過佢 繼續打我既機 同fd吹水<br />\n個日凌晨就開始黎料<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「其實我對你黎講都唔係咁重要啫 你連搵都唔搵我」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「又係你叫我唔好搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你可以繼續同你班fd吹水 開心啦？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「屌同你嗌交唔開心啫 我唔洗係佢地面前好似死老豆咁款掛 又唔關人地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你已經唔再愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知講乜撚野好 驚喜又係我整比佢<br />\n平時佢發我脾氣又係我氹返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣先可以令佢似返個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e99a0894ad44b4752a80e0b6400c0cf118ff9d4","tid":32393,"uid":24672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬係咪冇人撩唔開心😭😭😭<br />\n利申絲打咪一天都光晒</blockquote><br />\n紅巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f029b19f395d1760db1a0d9d903b25a03672aa63","tid":32393,"uid":24672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日覺得我男朋友係一個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多係多條撚<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n1. 我係唔撚信星座既 佢就成日睇星座乜乜乜<br />\n睇下我同佢夾唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲同我解釋乜野叫星盤 話我只係太陽雙魚 上升係天秤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲要屌返我話我無知<br />\n<br />\n2. 每次傾到食咩 次次都係我諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =男友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你想食咩呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「無所謂 你揀啦」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「日本野？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「唔想食」<br />\n<img src=\"/a